start a fire and cook.

701
00:42:34,239 --> 00:42:36,360
You need to cook
four dishes and one soup.

702
00:42:36,439 --> 00:42:37,479
The company that
prepares a complete meal first wins.

703
00:42:37,560 --> 00:42:37,959
Sure.

704
00:42:38,040 --> 00:42:38,760
Let's do it here.
